### Fox — XP Bonus (Special Mechanic)

Because there is no vanilla potion effect for XP gain, the Fox passive is implemented as a custom event hook rather than a status effect. It is the only companion that works this way.

**Implementation approach:**
- Hook into the `LivingEntity` experience drop event (Fabric API: `ServerLivingEntityEvents` or equivalent)
- Hook into the block break XP drop event
- When the event fires, check if the player has a following (non-sitting) tamed Fox within 24 blocks
- If so, multiply the XP drop amount by **x2** before it is applied
- This is a one-time multiplier per drop event, not a stacking buff
- Does not apply when the fox is sitting

